dex":"1","objecttype":"family","objectid":"61979","primarylink":0,"itemstate":"approved","href":"/boardgamefamily/61979/players-two-player-only-games","canonical_link":"https://boardgamegeek.com/boardgamefamily/61979/players-two-player-only-games"},{"name":"Series: Quarriors Pool Building system","sortindex":"1","objecttype":"family","objectid":"12425","primarylink":0,"itemstate":"approved","href":"/boardgamefamily/12425/series-quarriors-pool-building-system","canonical_link":"https://boardgamegeek.com/boardgamefamily/12425/series-quarriors-pool-building-system"}],"videogamebg":[],"boardgamesubdomain":[],"boardgameaccessory":[],"cardset":[]},"linkcounts":{"boardgamedesigner":2,"boardgamesolodesigner":0,"boardgameartist":0,"boardgamepublisher":1,"boardgamedeveloper":0,"boardgamegraphicdesigner":0,"boardgamesculptor":0,"boardgameeditor":0,"boardgamewriter":0,"boardgameinsertdesigner":0,"boardgamehonor":0,"boardgamecategory":5,"boardgamemechanic":3,"boardgameexpansion":0,"boardgameversion":1,"expandsboardgame":0,"boardgameintegration":1,"contains":0,"containedin":0,"reimplementation":0,"reimplements":0,"boardgamefamily":6,"videogamebg":0,"boardgamesubdomain":0,"boardgameaccessory":0,"cardset":0},"secondarynamescount":0,"alternatenamescount":0,"primaryname":{"nameid":"2288618","name":"Marvel Dice Masters: Secret Wars","sortindex":"1","primaryname":"1","translit":"Marvel Dice Masters: Secret Wars"},"alternatenames":[],"description":"<p><em><strong>Dice Masters</strong></em> brings Collectible Dice Building to the tabletop with this award-winning competitive game set in the Marvel universe!</p>\n\n<p><em>Dice Masters</em> is a global hit from WizKids. It uses the same proprietary Dice Building Game platform designed by Mike Elliott and Eric M. Lang.</p>\n\n<p>Each Countertop Display Contains 8 Draft Packs. Draft Packs contain cards and dice that can be added to your collection as normal but are ALSO optimized for draft! Whether you&rsquo;re drafting a team of heroes that normally appear together in comics, or you&rsquo;re focusing on your favorite type of energy, there will be TONS of ways to draft this set! With more than 35 heroes and villains, this set is perfect for veteran players or beginners!</p>\n\n<p>Brand new teams will make their Dice Masters debut! Players will get to collect Doom's minions, the heroes of Battleworld, and cosmic entities in all new ways! Even if they&rsquo;re already in your Dice Masters collection &ndash; these heroes will play like you&rsquo;ve never seen them before! Draft Packs are a fan-favorite format for Dice Masters!</p>\n\n<p>With over 150 different cards (and their dice!) to collect, this set will help you bring some Uncanny excitement to the tabletop!</p>\n\n<p><em>&mdash;description from the publisher</em></p>\n\n","wiki":"<p><strong>Contents</strong></p>\n\n<p>Each Marvel Dice Masters: Secret Wars Draft Pack contains the following:</p>\n\n<p>3 FULL ART Basic Action Cards!<br />\n12 FULL ART Character or Action Cards!<br />\nRandomly inserted FOIL cards!<br />\n24 dice (2 to match each character or action card)<br />\n1 rules insert</p>\n\n","website":{"url":false},"imageid":"7482656","images":{"thumb":"https://cf.geekdo-images.com/5FfR6dv1W6FM2hHpgFWAkg__small/img/dUhDfLJXVcQsbNPny3wLMJjsxXA=/fit-in/200x150/filters:strip_icc()/pic7482656.jpg","micro":"https://cf.geekdo-images.com/5FfR6dv1W6FM2hHpgFWAkg__micro/img/EcINn_J_XGohYcswUm9uCsiBGlM=/fit-in/64x64/filters:strip_icc()/pic7482656.jpg","square":"https://cf.geekdo-images.com/5FfR6dv1W6FM2hHpgFWAkg__square/img/ppaw6e1ecxtIWY6Bp7aUT19wqps=/75x75/filters:strip_icc()/pic7482656.jpg","tallthumb":"https://cf.geekdo-images.com/5FfR6dv1W6FM2hHpgFWAkg__tallthumb/img/yR61fPi6ssnFVQBqyfTRc-jYaHY=/fit-in/75x125/filters:strip_icc()/pic7482656.jpg","previewthumb":"https://cf.geekdo-images.com/5FfR6dv1W6FM2hHpgFWAkg__previewthumb/img/YDvCyC2Et_uf84I-oi6Jn56dWG4=/fit-in/300x320/filters:strip_icc()/pic7482656.jpg","square200":"https://cf.geekdo-images.com